    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You project a sphere of frigid energy towards your foe, freezing them in a layer of ice. Make a spell attack roll against the target's AC, dealing 6d6 cold damage (double on a critical hit) and the target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.VcDeM8A5oI6VqhbM]{Restrained} on a hit. This Restrained condition lasts for 1 round or until the target is hit with an attack, which shatters the ice. The creature can @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.SkZAQRkLLkmBQNB9]{Escape} normally against your spell DC on its turn.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.psGxrhfZh7G9aNoO]{Spell Effect: Cryo Blast}</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d6.</p>"
